 1411.3]}, {"text": "disposal activities and nullifies EITF 94-3, Liability Recognition for Certain Employee Termination Benefits and", "bbox": [143.8, 1415.3, 1094.2, 1436.3]}, {"text": "51", "bbox": [608.6, 1465.8, 629.4, 1486.6]}]}